  "original_title": "\u0b95\u0bbe\u0bb2\u0bbf \u0bb0\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bae\u0baf\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0ba4\u0bc1\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bbe\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bbf\u0b9a\u0bcd \u0b9a\u0bc2\u0b9f\u0bc1 :\u00a0 \u0b92\u0bb0\u0bc1\u0bb5\u0bb0\u0bcd \u0baa\u0bb2\u0bbf - \u0b87\u0bb0\u0bc1\u0bb5\u0bb0\u0bcd \u0baa\u0b9f\u0bc1\u0b95\u0bbe\u0baf\u0bae\u0bcd",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Firing in Galli Rathgam : One killed, two injured",
      "author": "T Yuwaraj",
      "body_lines": [
        "A 45-year-old man has died in a shooting incident in Ratgama area.",
        "Police said that one person was killed and two others were admitted to the hospital in the firing incident that took place in Rathgama-Kammedegoda area of \u200b\u200bGalle.",
        "In this case, it is noteworthy that a 51-year-old man was shot dead last night in Kotanchenai."
      ],
